      "name": "ImageMagick Service",
      "description": "OSCAR service for lightweight image processing with ImageMagick. For every input image, it generates a grayscale PNG, an edge-enhanced PNG, and a JSON file with width, height, brightness, contrast, and edge-density metrics. It supports both asynchronous storage-driven execution and synchronous invocations.",
